name: vbs22-avs-01
hint: Find shots showing one person playing a guitar (other people but no other musicians may be visible).

name: vbs22-avs-02
hint: Find shots of one or more persons balancing on a bar, railing, rope or slackline, without any device under their feet.

name: vbs22-avs-04
hint: Find shots of someone riding a horse or sitting on a horse (living animal).

name: vbs22-avs-05
hint: Find shots taken from any vehicle driving inside a tunnel, requiring part of the vehicle being visible.

name: vbs22-avs-06
hint: Find outdoor shots showing a teddy bear (toy).

name: vbs22-avs-07
hint: Find shots of a waterfall, without people.

name: vbs22-avs-09
hint: Find shots of one or more decorated trees (not just branches) that are not lit (inside or outside).

name: vbs22-avs-10
hint: Find shots of someone with their hands on a camera (not e.g. a phone-like device), filming or taking/preparing to take a picture.
